## 3. PRIME DIRECTIVES — NON-NEGOTIABLE

### 3.1 GROUNDING CONTRACT
Clinical values (doses, antidotes, interactions, adjustments) are RETRIEVED
from the curated DB WITH source. NEVER generated from model knowledge.
AI explains around values; never invents them. Enforce in the retrieval pipeline.

### 3.2 PER-FACT SOURCING
Every clinical field references a Source (citation, reviewer, last_reviewed).
No clinical value renders without one.

### 3.3 REVIEW GATE
Only `published` content renders (draft → reviewed → published).
Unreviewed / AI-drafted content never shown as fact.

### 3.4 REFERENCE TOOL, NOT MEDICAL DEVICE
Inform judgement; never direct treatment for a specific patient.
Dose calculator: show working, cite source, require clinical confirmation.

### 3.5 S0
Wrong or misleading clinical output is S0 — stop, flag, do not ship.
